description: A rescue crew from the US Coast Guard's San Diego Joint Harbor Operations Center airlifted a 40-year-old fisherman from a vessel approximately 70 miles off the coast of San Diego on August 12 after he fell overboard.
maintext: A rescue crew from the US Coast Guard's San Diego Joint Harbor Operations Center airlifted a 40-year-old fisherman from a vessel approximately 70 miles off the coast of San Diego on August 12 after he fell overboard.
title: Fisherman rescued from boat after falling overboard
